    "raw": "<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"kkp\">\n<style>\n.kkp{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto}\n.kkp .kkp-lead{font-size:1.18rem;line-height:1.5;max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 .4rem}\n.kkp .kkp-lead.kkp-kicker{font-weight:700}\n.kkp .kkp-label{font-size:.74rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;opacity:.55;margin:2rem 0 .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:1rem}\n.kkp .kkp-card{display:block;border:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;background:rgba(150,150,160,.05);transition:transform .15s ease,border-color .15s ease}\n.kkp .kkp-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:#e5462e}\n.kkp .kkp-card img,.kkp .kkp-ph{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover;display:block}\n.kkp .kkp-ph{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#23232e 0%,#3a2230 100%)}\n.kkp .kkp-txt{padding:.7rem .8rem .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-title{font-weight:700;font-size:.96rem;line-height:1.25}\n.kkp .kkp-sub{font-size:.8rem;opacity:.68;margin-top:.28rem;line-height:1.35}\n.kkp .kkp-cta{margin-top:2.4rem;padding-top:1.1rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);font-size:1.02rem}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a{color:#e5462e;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a:hover{text-decoration:underline}\n</style>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-lead kkp-kicker\">Nobody asked the artists before they scraped our work into a dataset.</p>\n<p class=\"kkp-lead\">So this isn't a hype page. It's a working creative's field manual for the synthetic age. How to use these tools without surrendering taste, judgment, or your community's trust. The thesis is Both Hands Full. Build human capacity at the same speed you build machine capacity.</p>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Start here</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/01/24/both-hands-full/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/MASTER-Blog-header.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Both Hands Full\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Both Hands Full</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">What creatives actually need to know about AI.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/05/15/your-taste-is-your-moat/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ai-creatives-krug.jpeg?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Your taste is your moat\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Your taste is your moat</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Why judgment beats creativity once generation is cheap.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/05/16/make-culture-not-content/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/06-mycelial-action-network.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Make Culture, Not Content\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Make Culture, Not Content</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">A field manual for the synthetic age.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Practice and workflow</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/06/13/speak-it-into-existence-ai-voice-first-workflows/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/03-both-hands-full-thesis.jpg?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Speak it into existence\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Speak it into existence</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Voice-first AI workflows that catch richer thinking.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/06/04/ai-keynote-slides-visual-workflow/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/01-blog-hero-taste-before-prompts.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Slides need taste first\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Slides need taste first</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">My visual workflow, the bad batch included.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/06/03/agent-orchestrators-creative-insurgents-the-new-stack/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/12-ai-is-a-mirror.jpg?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Agent orchestrators\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Agent orchestrators</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Orchestrating AI without losing authorship.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/05/24/ai-mindset-creative-paradigm/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/IMG_8053-scaled.jpg?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"The AI mindset\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">The AI mindset</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Thinking with machines, keeping the human weirdness.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-cta\">Browse the full <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/category/ai-creatives/\">AI for Creatives</a> archive, or bring it to your team with <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/generative-ai-services/\">the AI Upgrade training</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->",
